根据你的 Python 代码，这是对应的 curl 命令：

```bash
# 首先将图片转换为 base64（如果还没有）
IMAGE_BASE64=$(base64 -w 0 your_image.jpg)

# 发送请求
curl -X POST http://180.184.148.170:8000/v1/chat/completions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer empty" \
  -d '{
    "model": "kimi-k2",
    "messages": [
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "这张图片里描述了什么内容？"
          },
          {
            "type": "image_url",
            "image_url": {
              "url": "data:image/jpeg;base64,'"$IMAGE_BASE64"'"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "max_tokens": 2048
  }'
```

